{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41ab9cbf61","title":"一家贫农——访问越南通讯：《人民战争花最红》之二","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f8d45ff9eb","index":0,"year":1966,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"41ab9cbf61"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b7c521cc4","name":"人民战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","name":"红旗一九六六年第二期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"f050e3857c","name":"魏巍"}]},"publication_details":{"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f3e1ef177c","type":"paragraph","text":"家货农","index":0,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"89f7453966","type":"paragraph","text":"——黄圈越南通部：《人民战导花最红》之二","index":1,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"4ae55825c3","type":"paragraph","text":"魏蔬","index":2,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"8e694c0f1b","type":"paragraph","text":"江水穿过熟郁郁的山口直湾平原，奔葬苍苍，汽车在夜色里忽然颜起来。借着暗淡","index":3,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"edd0437c86","type":"paragraph","text":"正像是从群山里跃然而出的一条苍龙的丹光，我看看外面，大大小小的炸弹玩愈","index":4,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"2338451f62","type":"paragraph","text":"我们在桥上缓缓走去。一面察看这座桥来愈多。有的山坡也被炸施了，石头滚落在","index":5,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"171d32be49","type":"paragraph","text":"在夜色里雄伟的姿影，一面察看两早高登的路面上。经验告诉我，这是故人的炸重点。","index":6,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d429e104b4","type":"paragraph","text":"群山，一切都显得无比威严。听听脚下的江一间，果然前面不远就是W桥了","index":7,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9d430fc31b","type":"paragraph","text":"水，江水并不暗哗，但却隐隐传出深沉有力“哦，W桥”我的精神立刻为之一振","index":8,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f43d406bef","type":"paragraph","text":"的涛声。听说，在战斗最激烈的两天里，这不自禁地赋出声来。我早就听说，这是一座","index":9,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"ab59aae7a3","type":"paragraph","text":"里曾击落二十八架改机。我在想，当这些敌英雄的桥。在我们来到以而，这座桥已经被少则上儿架多则成百架的美国飞机袭炸了三","index":10,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b373a35767","type":"paragraph","text":"机冒着黑烟纷纷垫地的时候，该是多么壮观","index":11,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e684836af4","type":"paragraph","text":"的景象！难道这是白宫的老爷们所曾料到的十六次，而这座桥却仍旧塑然屹立在浓烟","index":12,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7c406ce3cf","type":"paragraph","text":"么不，他们没有料到。因为在他们的眼睛里，烈火中。并且，就在这座桥的四周，有整整四十架敌机落地装烧，还有不少的飞就被活","index":13,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d3579eb848","type":"paragraph","text":"这不过是地图上的-座普通的渡桥。他们不","index":14,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7005078f8c","type":"paragraph","text":"知道一座普通的渡桥，因为拥有英雄的人，它活生摄。（等到写这篇记事的时候，听说那","index":15,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"017a059eea","type":"paragraph","text":"就变成了一座隐伏着怒火的强大堡垒，一座里击落的敌机，已经不是四十架而是六十架了。）","index":16,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0beadf93d5","type":"paragraph","text":"在烈风火雨中镇静而威严的“钓鱼台”我们决定立刻下车步行，好更真切地看","index":17,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"66bf33193b","type":"paragraph","text":"围绕者这座桥，产生了多少动人心他的","index":18,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"1c57d7bb31","type":"paragraph","text":"故事呵看它，这座英雄的桥。","index":19,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"58ebf3e68e","type":"paragraph","text":"沿着山间公路走了不远，就看见一带江","index":20,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c030ed8dfc","type":"paragraph","text":"然而，我愿意首先叙说的，却是一家贫水在藤陇的月色里发着白光。人们份诉我，","index":21,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0f543ac838","type":"paragraph","text":"农。也许它可以回答：为什么桥能够在烈","index":22,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5d05d16523","type":"paragraph","text":"这就是D江。这是被约束在黑森森的群山里","index":23,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0a5e5038ef","type":"paragraph","text":"请问越通讯《人民战争花最红》之一：《飞机也","index":24,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"2cd501f171","type":"paragraph","text":"的一条激水。它势如奔马一般，正好在这里","index":25,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b8ddc88e04","type":"paragraph","text":"怕民兵》，发表在《人民日报》1965年12月25日","index":26,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"73c0fce239","type":"paragraph","text":"第B版。穿过一个险暖的山口。W桥就横在山口上。","index":27,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"50a54d845a","type":"paragraph","text":"红旗杂志·52（总110）","index":28,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"4c9e39dd00","type":"paragraph","text":"激流里向军舰奇力游去。有一个女民兵吴氏火中昂然吃立？也许它付以回答：人民战争","index":29,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"08ff2a83c8","type":"paragraph","text":"选（我在上篇文章里曾经提到她），因水急浪的花朵，在什么人的心里开得最美最红","index":30,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e44d0b8f12","type":"paragraph","text":"大，被大浪打昏了，又漂回到江岸：但她刚","index":31,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c6cd02a877","type":"paragraph","text":"刚醒转来，陆了儿口水，就又跳在奔腾的江这是发生在五月末尾的一次战斗。出于","index":32,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7f8df88cf6","type":"paragraph","text":"水里游过去了。还有一个发电厂的电工，也数机-次又一次遗到修重的损失，这些胆快","index":33,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"40425c850e","type":"paragraph","text":"游到军职上代替负伤的电工。质刻问，这只而获猎的飞赋们，就想出一条鬼主意：他们","index":34,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"daf4994c86","type":"paragraph","text":"江面上的活动堡垒，跑火又轰鸣起来，炮筒在装炸时总是向海的方向循冲：即便被打推，","index":35,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7c7e3c81d2","type":"paragraph","text":"指向关空展开更加想热的战斗。在这同时也可以落在海里，等待直升飞机来救。这天，","index":36,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"53a3d38831","type":"paragraph","text":"村子里的群众也都忙碌起来，有的忙着给民当敌机正这样耐神美炸桥的时候，忽然江中魏开一道浪花，从海上沿江而上开来了","index":37,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"699861bdbc","type":"paragraph","text":"兵做饭，有的驾着小船把啤酒和概子送上军","index":38,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d138af4c78","type":"paragraph","text":"。尽管弹片不断地刷刷地落到江面上，但一条越南军舰。这条军职正好对准你冲的敌机猛烈开火，给故机造成了致命的威胁。为","index":39,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f68b1f8098","type":"paragraph","text":"是运送弹药、运送饮料相接救析员的小脂，","index":40,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e27612f2ab","type":"paragraph","text":"化然一只接一只地间看军现前进。直到军期广摆脱不利的处境，敌机也就向这条车规折","index":41,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"79ad07b15d","type":"paragraph","text":"驶出自己商防区，民兵们还在江岸上不含地命地展开攻击。又是投炸弹，又是发射火器","index":42,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"3d232116d2","type":"paragraph","text":"追着它，跟着它，护送着它。这是一幅多么和导驰，项塑间，军舰四周都是腾起的水程。这条军舰十分镇定英勇，在奔腾的D江里忽","index":43,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f885bfebb2","type":"paragraph","text":"动人的人民战争的图画呵","index":44,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d5afd60ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"我所要讲的一家贫农的故事，就是在这进忽退，宛如一座威风藻擦的活动堡垒，不","index":45,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"40eea8d61a","type":"paragraph","text":"场战半单发生的。这个村子里有一个老贫农，时地向着附冲下来的敌机喷发春猛烈的炮","index":46,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"45dfefa512","type":"paragraph","text":"名叫吴寿菌，已经六十四岁了。他有五个儿火。但是后来因为军肌摘，中了一发火箭","index":47,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"71f532f280","type":"paragraph","text":"了，大儿子早已参军，下剩的四个儿子，过冒起烟来。现上的炮于也有不少负伤。也就","index":48,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5884dc9a61","type":"paragraph","text":"次全部上了军。弟兄四个合使一门高射炮，是在这最危急的时刻，出现了一场民兵保卫军舰的惊心动晚的携斗。","index":49,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5343c794d1","type":"paragraph","text":"有的装弹，有的开炮，打得十分英男。老人","index":50,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"3251d537ff","type":"paragraph","text":"最小的儿了吴寿六——大家都亲热地叫他六当时，在岸上指挥民兵作战的，是一他","index":51,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f725bb7f60","type":"paragraph","text":"儿，连续负伤两次都不下军舰，直到第三次二十一岁的姑娘。她名叫院此筛，是这个风","index":52,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7109bc31b5","type":"paragraph","text":"负了重伤英勇辆牡。小六儿的两个母哥也光的民兵队长。（她已经是我的熟朋友了，可情","index":53,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"72dcbd8894","type":"paragraph","text":"荣负伤。当他们英勇奋战时，老人正在社里此处不能详细描写她。）她正指挥着两个民兵","index":54,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"101ac96200","type":"paragraph","text":"喂精，听到儿子的伤亡，一步也没离开自己连同改机战斗。她见军现中弹，立即一面指择民兵射击俯冲的敌机，来拖护军肥；一","index":55,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"11aed06c43","type":"paragraph","text":"的岗位。直到给六儿送葬，他才去了。人们","index":56,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f76356540b","type":"paragraph","text":"怕这位年适的老人悲伤过度，我人操，而面指挥男女民兵登上军职，去救护伤员并代","index":57,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f616e6b0de","type":"paragraph","text":"他却拒绝别人来扶。并直，在基地的道掉会替负伤的炮手们。声令下，男女民兵们，有的驾起小船向军规猛划，有的跳在D江的","index":58,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"74ed3d16be","type":"paragraph","text":"上，老人硬是没有掉下·“消眼拍1966年第2期","index":59,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"770a2e67a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（总111）·53。","index":60,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"1bdafb3fdc","type":"paragraph","text":"子所作的黄献。老人兴奋得烟也顾不比抽了，这是怎样的一个家座，怎样的一位老","index":61,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"07a84909ed","type":"paragraph","text":"把点着的纸烟往烟灰缸上一放，就谈起他的人呵！","index":62,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"4158c25f01","type":"paragraph","text":"儿子来了。他告诉我们：他的大儿子在抗法我是多么渴望能够亲眼看一看他。到达","index":63,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"1b9927a75e","type":"paragraph","text":"战争时就参军去了，并且“参加过要边府战这个地方的第三大，我们就到他家里去了。","index":64,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"778b904ea4","type":"paragraph","text":"役”，他的大儿娘妇也参加了工作，对他非常那是一个雨夜。他的老伴说，她在社里喂猪","index":65,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"2cf497fa89","type":"paragraph","text":"孝顺：他的二儿子原来在军队上当炮手，复还没回来呢。我们等子一会儿，也不见回。","index":66,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"82e1ef612b","type":"paragraph","text":"员回来在碳米广当工人；他的三儿了在太原夜已经很深了。相陪的人催我们回去。我具","index":67,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"443cd148d5","type":"paragraph","text":"工业区当工人，最近也回来搞农业来了。说好带着非常遗械的心情，在蒲满的雨声里离","index":68,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"15e30fa98e","type":"paragraph","text":"到这里，他笑了一笑开了这个村庄.....","index":69,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c8546aa3e6","type":"paragraph","text":"“光我们家就有四个党员”","index":70,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"fb8901918f","type":"paragraph","text":"“都是谁？”我笑着问。没想到，过了一天，我们却意外地看到","index":71,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d6caf6b365","type":"paragraph","text":"“你看，”他伸着手指，“老大家两门儿，了他。","index":72,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"dd4b7b5b07","type":"paragraph","text":"还有老四和我们的六儿。”这是一个炎热的下午。我们正坐在一户","index":73,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"ab0ad430d6","type":"paragraph","text":"“六儿本来是团员，他牡那天才追认是农家探着汗面谈话，吴寿商和他的老伴，一","index":74,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0467ec316e","type":"paragraph","text":"党员的。”吴寿商的老件补充说，“在墓上追人手里提着两个绿度儿的大都子来了。他们","index":75,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"104bb6b884","type":"paragraph","text":"停他的时候，连他的叔权都称他是吴寿六是顶着大大的太阳，从二十延外赶来看我们","index":76,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f9880957e5","type":"paragraph","text":"同志。”的。老人的老代是前天雨夜我们在一益小油","index":77,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"34065f9223","type":"paragraph","text":"这时，我看见老人放在烟灰缸上的纸烟灯下看见过的。她比寿商老人小两岁，今年","index":78,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"2bfc0a3287","type":"paragraph","text":"已经想灭，连忙拿起打火机影独点者。老人已经六十二了。她今天还特意换了一件比较","index":79,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"aa3917e1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"究克有些上年纪了，由于他的话被别人打断，干净的棕紫色的上衣。可是，只要看一看她","index":80,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"bdb08863e7","type":"paragraph","text":"抽了两口烟，拍起头望望众人，时糖了下-·双隆超粗筋的赤脚，就前以想见她","index":81,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c5ccd4f0eb","type":"paragraph","text":"“我，我刚才讲到第儿个了？一生世经过了多少辛劳。寿商老人穿着抗","index":82,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5d9ac5f4d8","type":"paragraph","text":"讲到第四个了。”大家笑着说。战鞋，棕色的三婆衫已被汗水浸得褪了颜色。","index":83,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d2c3d361b3","type":"paragraph","text":"“对，对，讲到老四了。”他留着越南老人喜爱留的平头，虽然头发已经花白，但却行动敏捷，精神活跃。他把两","index":84,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"ab1849f117","type":"paragraph","text":"抱藏地笑了一笑。接香告诉我们，老","index":85,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0c7fdd0ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"四也在军队上当过炮于，现在是接兵连长。个大椰子往地上一放，就说：“那天晚上你们到我家去，我到社里喂猪去了，很对不起！","index":86,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d3e180e4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗那大，他情社里的精子毒了，正在社里","index":87,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8