,"index":99,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"2090613507","type":"paragraph","text":"子也没有别的。他就是喜欢书，喜欢交朋大的眼睛含着微笑，显得非常漂亮聪颖。","index":100,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"55dd0518f3","type":"paragraph","text":"友，出去的时候，衣服喜欢穿得整齐一些。“他是个乖孩子。“老妈妈说，“不光全家","index":101,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9449c302cd","type":"paragraph","text":"他还特别疼爱七妹妹，每天晚上回来，都教喜欢他，全村人都喜欢他。他是村里团支部的","index":102,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7e9a7deb02","type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹念书。他每月的工资不算多，除了给我委员，轴性时候，好多男女青年都哭啦。..","index":103,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7a9c677f65","type":"paragraph","text":"买烟打油，其余的都供给妹妹上学。.”从老妈妈的叙说里，我们知道，六儿在","index":104,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"18685aa546","type":"paragraph","text":"我转过脸问寿酶老人：七年级上就停了学，在村供销社当售货员。","index":105,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b70409017d","type":"paragraph","text":"“听说六儿性的时候，你正在社用喂可是他思想开朗，他说，停儿年再上学有什","index":106,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0964abaed1","type":"paragraph","text":"猪？”么要紧！供销社一部分卖百货，部分卖烟、","index":107,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d0f493a429","type":"paragraph","text":"“对，对，”老人点头说，“那关我正在社油。本来由两个售货员管，另一个不在时，","index":108,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"633a67d382","type":"paragraph","text":"里喂猪。有人跑来说：“吴寿商！你的四个孩他就跑来跑去一个人十。他还在村子里扣任","index":109,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"82cc861091","type":"paragraph","text":"子都上军顺了！”我说：“他们有他们的住务，治安工作，敌机一来，他就拿着喇叭赋，格","index":110,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f36bdabcd1","type":"paragraph","text":"我有我的任务，没有什么可大惊小怪的。过促大家下防空。飞机一走，他又跑到供销","index":111,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"bc15cb4066","type":"paragraph","text":"一时，又有人跑来我绑担架的东西，我就社售货。晚上还去文化补习班教书。临参加","index":112,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d344102dc5","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“有人负伤了吗？他们就告诉我，老网负战斗那天，他正拿着喇叭赋呢，一听军职遇","index":113,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"bf07dcfa58","type":"paragraph","text":"伤了，六儿也负伤了。他们没有收说六儿辆险，就急忆把喇叭交给别人，说：“我要到军","index":114,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"628fb63866","type":"paragraph","text":"性了。这时候，我打了一个寒味，觉着跟平视去！”还说：“你们等着看吧，我会表现出勇","index":115,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"cadbd81d6f","type":"paragraph","text":"时很不一样。可是我守着猪圈，一步也没有敢来的！”他上了军舰，哥哥们打炮，他就在","index":116,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e2db016d1d","type":"paragraph","text":"动。我不能商开！旁边装弹。他还让哥哥教自己打炮。他的下","index":117,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d651cc3bc1","type":"paragraph","text":"“这是为什么？”有人插嘴问。巴被弹片打伤，揭出手前包扎了一下，一边","index":118,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"56ed29bed7","type":"paragraph","text":"“为什么！这是我们社黑的整整五十口着血，边坚持战斗。他的哥哥要他下","index":119,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"78052f0993","type":"paragraph","text":"猪呀！”老人望着大家，“我要离开，飞机来去，急得他什么似的连连向哥哥作挥说：“我","index":120,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"010bf058c3","type":"paragraph","text":"炸了，就没有人把猪栏打开，这些猪得统统的好可哥，我拜拜你们，叫我千方留在这里","index":121,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b980f68947","type":"paragraph","text":"炸死！”吧”他打出了第二排炮弹时，敌人的弹片又","index":122,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e63e76f8fe","type":"paragraph","text":"老人神色激动，把手里的烟又往烟灰缸打伤了他的左脚，他没有倒下，仍继续向","index":123,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"3e996d851b","type":"paragraph","text":"上一放敌机开火。后来，一发火箭射来，弹片打市","index":124,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7dc1d720f5","type":"paragraph","text":"“后来，又有人说：你的四个孩子，不了他的头部。他实在无法继续战斗了。可是","index":125,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"546ede9616","type":"paragraph","text":"是死了，就是衡了。我想，负了伤，国家给在滚滚的烟火里，他还向哥哥们行了个举手","index":126,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"4703f671de","type":"paragraph","text":"他治疗；就是性，国家也会好好安葬。我礼，表示告别，然后才倒在甲板上……","index":127,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5ce6c47b40","type":"paragraph","text":"（总113）·55°1966年第2期","index":128,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"bd0a21719d","type":"paragraph","text":"晚上的那个雨夜，在奔腾的D江边上的那座只有优恨美帝，如果美国飞机不来，我的儿","index":129,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7685a020f1","type":"paragraph","text":"茅屋。这座茅屋看来比村里其他的农舍要显子怎么会有的负伤有的性了呢！同志呀，","index":130,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9ffddf970b","type":"paragraph","text":"得低矮。可是就在这样的孝屋里，居住着一我给你说，这时候，我真惯怒得发抖，可是","index":131,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f032c20a0a","type":"paragraph","text":"户对革命对祖国多么思城而又多么坚强的象我不能哭。因为，这时候飞机走了，大家正","index":132,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"891c7d3b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"庭呵！在扬场，人很多；我要是哭了，就会影啊扬","index":133,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"6f7ded0b31","type":"paragraph","text":"谈起现在的生活，老人说场，更可能影响别人的情绪。我就呀附家里","index":134,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"488125a59d","type":"paragraph","text":"“困难是有，可是要比起从前就好得多人：统统不能哭！谁也不许哭！.....","index":135,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"de1020bd67","type":"paragraph","text":"了。我给同志说吧，八月革命前，我吴寿随","index":136,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5a8104f6ec","type":"paragraph","text":"“那天，也有不少人去安慰他。”老伴补充说。","index":137,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"cb73ae40f4","type":"paragraph","text":"没有--寸土地，几十年，我们两口都是给地“对，对，那天有不少人到猪圈来安感","index":138,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5d98ee03df","type":"paragraph","text":"主做苦工的·....”","index":139,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"8a0efb43d9","type":"paragraph","text":"“算啦，过去的事不要提啦！”老伴扭过我。”老人接着说，“我对多亲们讲：做父母","index":140,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9ce6727d62","type":"paragraph","text":"脸去。的谁不心疼孩子？六儿，也不是容易就养大的。可是，他是为祖国，为党，为人民辆性","index":141,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"08cad0b1d2","type":"paragraph","text":"“给中国局志讲谐怕什么，”老人看了老的。他辆性是他完成了白己的任务：我不能","index":142,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"038deb15b3","type":"paragraph","text":"伴一限。“后来我又给人挑东西。来回几十","index":143,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"1cb3fce600","type":"paragraph","text":"公里，换不到儿个钱。就这样，日本法西斯回家去，因为我的任务还没有完成。直到当","index":144,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"037ea4534f","type":"paragraph","text":"还在路上拦住我，不让我去。钱换不来，俄天晚上，有个姑娘来代替我喂猪，我才离开了猪圈。...","index":145,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"a70cba0b2b","type":"paragraph","text":"得孩子们唯唯地哭。遮得设法儿，我文去山我又问，","index":146,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0578b440b2","type":"paragraph","text":"里开荒，法国鬼子的飞机又来轰炸，一天到","index":147,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"d0135efd49","type":"paragraph","text":"晚钻防空洞。等到开出荒地，粮食还没有收“听说，给六儿送葬，你还不让人擦？”","index":148,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c13e25a7fe","type":"paragraph","text":"到手里，地主文跑来收租子了。”他激动起“是呀，”他点点头说，“你想。哭果暗略","index":149,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c5a0818955","type":"paragraph","text":"来，“这天地虽大，通得我吴寿商没有一条热势扶扶的多难看哪，我给人家讲：我知道","index":150,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"adaf91baad","type":"paragraph","text":"路可走呀！最后我不得不去.….”你们搜我，这是好意；是，你们看，我不哭","index":151,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"efebb20244","type":"paragraph","text":"“喉噪，你给同志们讲这些有什么用也不掉剂，我走得动，你们谁也不要来扶”","index":152,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"35651615bd","type":"paragraph","text":"老伴立刻文打断他，而耳显得有些激动了。说到这里，他指了指他的老样","index":153,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e6ba786a25","type":"paragraph","text":"“这些事三天三夜也讲不完“那天晚上，我们送葬回来，已经后飞","index":154,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9a80f88fad","type":"paragraph","text":"由于老伴儿次打断，老人对自己的身世夜了。省委的同志担心我们过于悲痛，把我","index":155,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e7eb4b1947","type":"paragraph","text":"也就不多说了。但是他的神色仍然十分激们接到办公室去安藏我们。我的老伴就说","index":156,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"77b620bc41","type":"paragraph","text":"动，他说：“请领导上放心。以后敌机再来，我就代替","index":157,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"363db874a9","type":"paragraph","text":"同志，你想想，我们还愿意走因头路，六儿去送炮弹我说：“不成！你还要照顾孙","index":158,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"dc0454240d","type":"paragraph","text":"再去过那样的生活吗？不，不，我们一定要子啤，再说你的身子也不太行，这个任务就","index":159,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"8283a6eb71","type":"paragraph","text":"打到底1”交给我1.....","index":160,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"ed7ffb3420","type":"paragraph","text":"寿商的老伴心事重重，偏过脸坐在那里，当老人谈着这些的时候，我的心被一种","index":161,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"08ec8035b6","type":"paragraph","text":"地今天儿次打断老人的谈话，可以想到，这无比强大的力量震撼着。我不禁又想起前天","index":162,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"cd27652dfa","type":"paragraph","text":"红旗杂点56·（总114）","index":163,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f8880f8bcc","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民对他们的坚决支持。说过以后，从其中有多少字酸事呵！虽然这些事没有细讲，","index":164,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c68b482d07","type":"paragraph","text":"手上脱下一个用敌人飞机残酸做成的银色顶我们也是可以猜到的吧。这个富能的绿色的","index":165,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"342a8a4d5c","type":"paragraph","text":"指，套在我的手指上。国土，整整被法国人压株了八十年！在这八","index":166,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"f1ebcb9af0","type":"paragraph","text":"我们把两位老人送出门外，送到裁种着十年中，越南人民真正是被榨得千干的。所","index":167,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"c493895daf","type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的龙骨色的小径上。我久久地望着他人说，过去由于人们吃不起威盐，甚至流止","index":168,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"712e4768f4","type":"paragraph","text":"们的背影，望着他们被终年的开水浸褪了色来的汗水都不是咸的。这是多么可怕的生","index":169,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"e729333ec5","type":"paragraph","text":"的衣堂，望着他们粗筋降起的求脚，心里不活！两位老人和千千万万的越南人民，就是","index":170,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"778503cd60","type":"paragraph","text":"禁默默地赋着：贫农们！对革命、对祖国、从这样的生活里走过来的。而今，越南人民","index":171,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"0e74c100f5","type":"paragraph","text":"对党思城不二的贫农们！今天，我又从你们好容易从法帝国主义铁蹄下得到了解放，万","index":172,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"7e14b86f45","type":"paragraph","text":"身上，着到了这块上地上深不可测的力量，恶的美带国卡义又把侵略的魔瓜伸向这个国","index":173,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"8142692425","type":"paragraph","text":"听到了这块土地上真正的心声。我深信，即家，企图重新来奴役他们。难怪一提这些","index":174,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"5651fbb84a","type":"paragraph","text":"使在你们的面前，横起一道红腾腾的火山，老人会那么倾激。是的，这是永远也不能再","index":175,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"6bfe60a4d0","type":"paragraph","text":"它也挡不住你们的去路呵！让它回来的旧生活！即使粉身碎骨也不能再走这样的回头路！“我们一定要打到底！”","index":176,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b6351eed30","type":"paragraph","text":"两位老人已经转过小径，渐新消尖在西","index":177,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"b74983d521","type":"paragraph","text":"蕉的绿丛里。我正待转过身来，这时候，猛这是寿商老人也是全体越商人民发自内心深处的呼声。","index":178,"publicationId":"fb71dfe8-41f8-40fc-be7e-de81d9bcab90","articleId":"41ab9cbf61"},{"id":"9e06ac2c0b","type":"paragraph","text":"然听见W桥方向，响起了一阵十分喀亮悦1最后，老人站起身来，托我们一定要向","index":179,"publicationId":"fb